Class RegView

  • java.lang.Object
    • cst8284.asgmt3.landRegistry.RegView

  • public class RegView
extends java.lang.Object
    This is the RegView class for the land registry application. This class is responsible to retrieve the user input and pass it to the controller class or get the response from the controller class and display the result Assignment 3 starter code provided by Prof. D. Houtman for use in CST8284 Assignment 3, due July 26, 2020. This code is for one-time use only during the Summer 2020 semester. (c) D. Houtman. All rights reserved
